learn-DeepCode
==============

This repository is a learning companion to HKUDS/DeepCode (https://github.com/HKUDS/DeepCode),
a multi-agent AI system for "Open Agentic Coding" — Paper2Code, Text2Web, and Text2Backend.

Upstream license: MIT (Copyright (c) 2025 Data Intelligence Lab @ HKU).
This learn-repo: MIT (Copyright (c) 2026 Ding-Ye).

Pedagogy inspired by shareAI-lab/learn-claude-code
(https://github.com/shareAI-lab/learn-claude-code): each chapter teaches one
upstream mechanism by progressively building a tiny re-implementation in Go.

This repo is NOT a fork or redistribution of DeepCode. The Go code here is
independently re-implemented from the architectural patterns documented in
the upstream Python source. Upstream source quotations under
upstream-readings/ are reproduced under fair-use for educational commentary.
